message.body: Yeah! Lets hang out tomorrow! Looking forward to it!
When are you going to be around tomorrow?
My bus gets in at 1215, i dont have any plans but was thinking of trying to get student rush tickets to see the NY philharmonic play a live score to Charlie Chaplin for tomorrow night
Cool. When do you need to get the tickets?
I just found out that they dont do saturday rush tickets. We should grab lunch tomorrow
Sounds good, give me a call when you get in tomorrow
My bus is really late, but should arrive in 40 min
Ok, no worries. Still wanna get lunch?
Let me know when you're getting off the bus
